<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:14:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>供应紧张之际，中国将在新加坡航展上展示国产客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</link><description>新加坡将于下周举办自新冠疫情边境限制结束以来首次举办亚洲最大的航空展，地区旅行将出现反弹，展会的军事方面将布满防御系统和紧张的武器买家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>香港当局在价值18亿美元的洗钱案中逮捕了七人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</link><description>香港当局周五表示，他们逮捕了 7 名涉嫌参与 18 亿美元洗钱案件的人，这是该金融中心有史以来规模最大的洗钱案件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商押注中国有望重新开放，并向香港大量发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</link><description>根据行业数据和贸易数据，澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商已将数百万瓶葡萄酒运往香港，押注中国将很快取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税并重振价值数亿美元的贸易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数冲向历史新高，美元承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-16/</link><description>周五，日本日经指数冲向历史新高，美国零售销售大幅下滑重振了六月降息的可能性，从而令美元承压，华尔街表现活跃，推动日经指数走高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 02:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>交易员权衡经济数据美元坚挺，日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-weigh-economic-data-yen-fragile-2024-02-16/</link><description>由于投资者评估了最新的经济数据以及对美联储 6 月降息的坚定预期，美元周五走强，有望连续第五周上涨，而日元则锚定在 150 美元兑 150 美元的关键水平附近。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 01:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-weigh-economic-data-yen-fragile-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：利率希望胜过经济恐慌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-15/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋岛国对美国拖延资助感到担忧，对中国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</link><description>美国战略盟友太平洋岛国的领导人对美国国会预算僵局越来越感到焦虑，这一僵局导致重要的新融资方案的批准被推迟，并警告说，中国正在积极寻求改变他们的忠诚度，包括对台湾的忠诚度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 20:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车表示，巴西可持续发展规则不应让汽车变得更加昂贵</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</link><description>大众汽车巴西业务负责人西罗·波索博姆 (Ciro Possobom) 表示，巴西旨在促进该国汽车行业可持续发展投资的新激励计划需要避免使车辆变得更加昂贵。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:14:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卢比奥敦促 SEC 阻止 Shein IPO，除非披露中国运营风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/rubio-urges-sec-block-shein-ipo-unless-china-operating-risk-disclosed-2024-02-15/</link><description>共和党参议员马可·卢比奥 (Marco Rubio) 要求美国证券交易委员会阻止 Shein 在纽约公开上市的申请，除非这家电子零售商进一步披露其业务运营以及在中国“开展业务的严重风险”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 17:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/rubio-urges-sec-block-shein-ipo-unless-china-operating-risk-disclosed-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>福特和通用汽车首席执行官愿意建立合作伙伴关系以与中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-ceo-open-working-with-rivals-compete-with-china-2024-02-15/</link><description>美国汽车制造商福特和通用汽车的首席执行官周四表示，随着中国竞争对手进军美国和欧洲市场，他们将考虑建立合作伙伴关系，以降低电动汽车技术成本。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 15:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-ceo-open-working-with-rivals-compete-with-china-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>在罗马争执中，Stellantis 首席执行官表示意大利工厂有未来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/amid-rome-spat-stellantis-ceo-says-italy-plants-have-future-2024-02-15/</link><description>Stellantis首席执行官卡洛斯·塔瓦雷斯(Carlos Tavares)周四表示，该汽车制造商将需要其所有意大利工厂来实现其在那里的长期生产目标，这一和解言论可能会缓解菲亚特汽车制造商与罗马之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:28:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/amid-rome-spat-stellantis-ceo-says-italy-plants-have-future-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国竞争的加剧，欧洲和美国汽车制造商竞相降低电动汽车成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-renault-race-cut-costs-make-evs-more-affordable-2024-02-15/</link><description>行业高管周四表示，在中国竞争对手的压力下，美国和欧洲主要汽车制造商正在大力削减电动汽车成本，以便获得与化石燃料车型相似的价格标签和利润率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-renault-race-cut-costs-make-evs-more-affordable-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>晚场秀将阿尔希拉尔推向亚洲CL四分之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/joos-brace-moves-ulsan-verge-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-15/</link><description>周二，亚历山大·米特罗维奇和阿卜杜拉·哈姆丹在补时阶段的进球帮助希拉尔队后来居上，以3-1击败伊朗队的10人塞帕汉队，向亚冠四分之一决赛又近了一步。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 12:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/joos-brace-moves-ulsan-verge-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>数百万人从农历新年旅行归来，预计中国将迎来寒流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cold-snap-expected-china-millions-return-lunar-new-year-trips-2024-02-15/</link><description>国家气象台周四表示，预计从本周末开始，一股寒流将席卷中国大部分地区，随着数百万人春节旅行归来，气温将下降高达20摄氏度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cold-snap-expected-china-millions-return-lunar-new-year-trips-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：强调科技主导的美国“例外主义”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-02-15/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-02-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>